items.title: Where To Watch Twilight

items.title: Sonic The Hedgehog 4 Has An Impossible Mission If The Franchise Is Bold Enough To Stick With Sonic 3's Ending
items.description: With the major plot developments in Sonic the Hedgehog 3's ending, the next film in the series will have a tough time rebuilding to the same level.
